            "body": "> Notice that this only errors on WSL. It didn't happen on native windows.\n\ndoes it error in WSL when the init.lua/gitignore are in WSL file system, or in the windows filesystem e.g. `/mnt/c/...`? \n\n[file operations from WSL on windows explanation](https://github.com/microsoft/WSL/issues/4197#issuecomment-604592340)\n\nTLDR: Store projects in the Linux file system (`/home/...`) rather than Windows drives (`/mnt/c/...`) for best performance in WSL2.",
